name: Evidence
description:
Evidence, is anything that you see, experience, read, or are told that causes you to believe that something is true or has really happened. MM college on bamboo, I animated it using Light Tricks and edited it with sound in Kinemaster.

This NFT features the music of Cut-Out “Now What” Cut-Out is a studio project by members of Pell Mell, Robert Beerman, Greg Freeman and Steve Fisk. This music is unreleased and is being used by permission.
